    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:30.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Collaboration Index Feed\n\nWhen a document becomes collaborative, the sharer creates a collaboration index feed at `ph:v2:collab:<docId>`, owned by the sharer's signer.\n\n## Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"docId\": \"doc-001\",\n  \"documentType\": \"powerhouse/budget-statement\",\n  \"name\": \"Q1 Budget\",\n  \"createdBy\": \"0xAlice_signer\",\n  \"collaborators\": [\n    {\n      \"address\": \"0xAlice_signer\",\n      \"opFeedTopic\": \"ph:v2:ops:0xalice_signer:doc-001\",\n      \"joinedAt\": \"2026-04-10T12:00:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"address\": \"0xBob_signer\",\n      \"opFeedTopic\": \"ph:v2:ops:0xbob_signer:doc-001\",\n      \"joinedAt\": \"2026-04-10T14:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-10T14:00:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n## Role\n\n- Acts as a directory: given `docId`, anyone can discover all participant op-feed topics\n- Only the creator can append \u2014 but collaborators can be added by updating the index\n- Each collaborator still owns their own ops feed; the index is a lookup table, not a merge point\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:30.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:30.000Z"
    }
  },
